main.tf-- main file where we write our code or all the actions happened
now "main.tf" files pulls the variable from variables.tf which pulls there values from terraform.tfvars
variables.tf----> it will have empty variable and terraform.tfvars-- just poppulate those variable
terraform.tfvars--> make sure when you create git repository, you always put your tfvars in git the ignore 
